    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your sniping is quick enough that you can fire a small volley unnoticed.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Expert Sniper, Rapid Shot, Stealth 6 ranks.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While hiding, you can make two ranged attacks at your highest attack bonus as a full-round action and then immediately use Stealth again. You take the normal penalties on your Stealth check to remain hidden. Effects that modify sniping apply to this full-round action. These attack rolls take a -2 penalty.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>You can fire only once when sniping.",
